                                show="replace"
                                linktype="simple">
                           <geogname normal="Rome (Roma province, Lazio, Italy), inhabited place           [7000874]">Rome</geogname>
                        </extref>, the latter end of the <extref href="https://www.thomasgray.org/resources/table.shtml#1740"
                                show="replace"
                                linktype="simple">
                           <date normal="174005" certainty="circa" era="ce" calendar="gregorian">Spring, 1740</date>
                        </extref>. after a 
								journey to <geogname normal="Frascati (Roma            province, Lazio, Italy), inhabited place [7007013]">Frescati</geogname> &amp; the Cascades of <extref href="https://www.thomasgray.org/resources/glplaces.shtml#Tivoli (Roma province,          Lazio, Italy), inhabited place [7006968]"
